[
	{
		"id": 0,
		"localized_name": "タイニー",
		"romanized_name": "Tiny",
		"model_path_hash": "2428915022803462192",
		"text": "た、大変ですボス！！\n「ヌルスラの鷹」がいません！",
		"voice_file": "VOICE_MAIN_221_036_01165",
		"still_path_hash": "5609327809530807165",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 1,
		"localized_name": "エルス",
		"romanized_name": "Els",
		"model_path_hash": "5033911810886101706",
		"text": "手錠をかけて、縛っておいたというのにか",
		"voice_file": "VOICE_MAIN_222_036_01166",
		"still_path_hash": "532943395044460292",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 2,
		"localized_name": "タイニー",
		"romanized_name": "Tiny",
		"model_path_hash": "2428915022803462192",
		"text": "それが、まだ逃亡用の魔物を隠していたみたいで……\n縄は食い破られ、手錠も壊されてました",
		"voice_file": "VOICE_MAIN_221_036_01167",
		"still_path_hash": "5609327809530807165",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 3,
		"localized_name": "エルス",
		"romanized_name": "Els",
		"model_path_hash": "5033911810886101706",
		"text": "ちっ……捕まった時の三下臭い態度は芝居だったか",
		"voice_file": "VOICE_MAIN_222_036_01168",
		"still_path_hash": "532943395044460292",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 4,
		"localized_name": "タイニー",
		"romanized_name": "Tiny",
		"model_path_hash": "2428915022803462192",
		"text": "ごめんなさい、王妃様ばっかり気にかけてて……\n私、やっぱり半人前です！",
		"voice_file": "VOICE_MAIN_221_036_01169",
		"still_path_hash": "5609327809530807165",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 5,
		"localized_name": "エルス",
		"romanized_name": "Els",
		"model_path_hash": "5033911810886101706",
		"text": "それは私もだが、反省するのは後だ！\n「ヌルスラの鷹」を探すぞ！",
		"voice_file": "VOICE_MAIN_222_036_01170",
		"still_path_hash": "532943395044460292",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 6,
		"localized_name": "レスナ",
		"romanized_name": "Resna",
		"model_path_hash": "6823802507187778884",
		"text": "……ねぇイザナちゃん。\nさっき走り去った影、なんだったんだろうね？",
		"voice_file": "VOICE_MAIN_001_036_01171",
		"still_path_hash": "2457375212832216718",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 7,
		"localized_name": "イザナ",
		"romanized_name": "Izana",
		"model_path_hash": "7061794453237574237",
		"text": "魔物のような人間のような……アタシたち、\n武道会で疲れてるから、見間違えたのかも……",
		"voice_file": "VOICE_MAIN_048_036_01172",
		"still_path_hash": "7010833269667927555",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 8,
		"localized_name": "ヴァレリア",
		"romanized_name": "Valeria",
		"model_path_hash": "8455227271865371244",
		"text": "あっ！　レスナ！！",
		"voice_file": "VOICE_MAIN_002_036_01173",
		"still_path_hash": "6891392099494261238",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 9,
		"localized_name": "レスナ",
		"romanized_name": "Resna",
		"model_path_hash": "6823802507187778884",
		"text": "ヴァレリア！　国王陛下から「九偉人図」を\nいただいたよ――って、そんなに急いでどうしたの？",
		"voice_file": "VOICE_MAIN_001_036_01174",
		"still_path_hash": "2457375212832216718",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 10,
		"localized_name": "エルス",
		"romanized_name": "Els",
		"model_path_hash": "5033911810886101706",
		"text": "逃亡犯の追跡中だ！\n魔物に乗って逃亡していると思われる。見ていないか？",
		"voice_file": "VOICE_MAIN_222_036_01175",
		"still_path_hash": "532943395044460292",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 11,
		"localized_name": "イザナ",
		"romanized_name": "Izana",
		"model_path_hash": "7061794453237574237",
		"text": "あっ……やっぱり見間違えじゃなかったんだ！",
		"voice_file": "VOICE_MAIN_048_036_01176",
		"still_path_hash": "7010833269667927555",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 12,
		"localized_name": "レスナ",
		"romanized_name": "Resna",
		"model_path_hash": "6823802507187778884",
		"text": "見ました！　あっちに走って行きました！",
		"voice_file": "VOICE_MAIN_001_036_01177",
		"still_path_hash": "2457375212832216718",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 13,
		"localized_name": "エルス",
		"romanized_name": "Els",
		"model_path_hash": "5033911810886101706",
		"text": "了解！　情報提供に感謝する！",
		"voice_file": "VOICE_MAIN_222_036_01178",
		"still_path_hash": "532943395044460292",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 14,
		"localized_name": "レスナ",
		"romanized_name": "Resna",
		"model_path_hash": "6823802507187778884",
		"text": "ま、待ってください、私たちも行きます！\n先導しますから！",
		"voice_file": "VOICE_MAIN_001_036_01179",
		"still_path_hash": "2457375212832216718",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 15,
		"localized_name": "ヌルスラの鷹",
		"romanized_name": "",
		"model_path_hash": "0",
		"text": "つっ、この野郎、いきなり転びやがって\n使えねえヤツだ！",
		"voice_file": "VOICE_MAIN_710_036_01180",
		"still_path_hash": "0",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 16,
		"localized_name": "ジョゼ",
		"romanized_name": "José",
		"model_path_hash": "0",
		"text": "魔物といえども仲間に対してその仕打ちとは……\nつくづく悪党のようだな",
		"voice_file": "VOICE_MAIN_223_036_01181",
		"still_path_hash": "1488533364831425921",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 17,
		"localized_name": "レスナ",
		"romanized_name": "Resna",
		"model_path_hash": "6823802507187778884",
		"text": "こっちです、みんな！",
		"voice_file": "VOICE_MAIN_001_036_01182",
		"still_path_hash": "2457375212832216718",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 18,
		"localized_name": "ヌルスラの鷹",
		"romanized_name": "",
		"model_path_hash": "0",
		"text": "なっ……まさか、ギヨームなのか？\nなんでてめえがこんなとこに……",
		"voice_file": "VOICE_MAIN_710_036_01183",
		"still_path_hash": "0",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 19,
		"localized_name": "ジョゼ",
		"romanized_name": "José",
		"model_path_hash": "0",
		"text": "……俺はそんな名前じゃない。悪を狩る仮面、\n賞金稼ぎのジョゼ・ダンブロシオだ",
		"voice_file": "VOICE_MAIN_223_036_01184",
		"still_path_hash": "1488533364831425921",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 20,
		"localized_name": "ヌルスラの鷹",
		"romanized_name": "",
		"model_path_hash": "0",
		"text": "ぐっ！　いいや、ふざけた格好してるが\nてめえは、確か、に……ぐふっ！",
		"voice_file": "VOICE_MAIN_710_036_01185",
		"still_path_hash": "0",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 21,
		"localized_name": "レスナ",
		"romanized_name": "Resna",
		"model_path_hash": "6823802507187778884",
		"text": "ジョゼさん……？",
		"voice_file": "VOICE_MAIN_001_036_01186",
		"still_path_hash": "2457375212832216718",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 22,
		"localized_name": "エルス",
		"romanized_name": "Els",
		"model_path_hash": "5033911810886101706",
		"text": "見つけたのか！？",
		"voice_file": "VOICE_MAIN_222_036_01187",
		"still_path_hash": "532943395044460292",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 23,
		"localized_name": "タイニー",
		"romanized_name": "Tiny",
		"model_path_hash": "2428915022803462192",
		"text": "はぁ、はぁっ……やっぱ、戦った後の\n全力疾走はキツい……",
		"voice_file": "VOICE_MAIN_048_036_01188",
		"still_path_hash": "5609327809530807165",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 24,
		"localized_name": "タイニー",
		"romanized_name": "Tiny",
		"model_path_hash": "2428915022803462192",
		"text": "あっ、変てこ仮面さん！",
		"voice_file": "VOICE_MAIN_221_036_01189",
		"still_path_hash": "5609327809530807165",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 25,
		"localized_name": "ジョゼ",
		"romanized_name": "José",
		"model_path_hash": "0",
		"text": "やあ、監察官の嬢ちゃん。\nこいつは俺が捕まえた。賞金は俺のものだね",
		"voice_file": "VOICE_MAIN_223_036_01190",
		"still_path_hash": "1488533364831425921",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 26,
		"localized_name": "タイニー",
		"romanized_name": "Tiny",
		"model_path_hash": "2428915022803462192",
		"text": "最初に捕まえたのは私たちなのに！\n美味しいとこだけ持ってくなんてずるいです！",
		"voice_file": "VOICE_MAIN_221_036_01191",
		"still_path_hash": "5609327809530807165",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 27,
		"localized_name": "エルス",
		"romanized_name": "Els",
		"model_path_hash": "5033911810886101706",
		"text": "タイニー、感謝こそすれ抗議する謂れはない。\n引き渡してもらえるか？　賞金は払おう",
		"voice_file": "VOICE_MAIN_222_036_01192",
		"still_path_hash": "532943395044460292",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 28,
		"localized_name": "ジョゼ",
		"romanized_name": "José",
		"model_path_hash": "0",
		"text": "ああ、もちろん。今度は逃げられないよう\nいつも以上にキツく捕まえておくんだね",
		"voice_file": "VOICE_MAIN_223_036_01193",
		"still_path_hash": "1488533364831425921",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 29,
		"localized_name": "エルス",
		"romanized_name": "Els",
		"model_path_hash": "5033911810886101706",
		"text": "うむ。では王宮へ戻ろう。王妃と共に牢に入れる。\nまたしっかり、事情聴取をしなくてはな",
		"voice_file": "VOICE_MAIN_222_036_01194",
		"still_path_hash": "532943395044460292",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 30,
		"localized_name": "ヴァレリア",
		"romanized_name": "Valeria",
		"model_path_hash": "8455227271865371244",
		"text": "また気絶者が増えたわね……\nキューンとヤドヴィガで精一杯だってのに",
		"voice_file": "VOICE_MAIN_002_036_01195",
		"still_path_hash": "6891392099494261238",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 31,
		"localized_name": "レスナ",
		"romanized_name": "Resna",
		"model_path_hash": "6823802507187778884",
		"text": "そっちも何かあったの？",
		"voice_file": "VOICE_MAIN_001_036_01196",
		"still_path_hash": "2457375212832216718",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 32,
		"localized_name": "ヴァレリア",
		"romanized_name": "Valeria",
		"model_path_hash": "8455227271865371244",
		"text": "うん。ま、それは王宮に着いたら話すわ！\nさあ行きましょ！",
		"voice_file": "VOICE_MAIN_002_036_01197",
		"still_path_hash": "6891392099494261238",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 33,
		"localized_name": "ジョゼ",
		"romanized_name": "José",
		"model_path_hash": "0",
		"text": "さて……任務達成だな。俺も賞金もらって、\nその金で１杯やりにでも行くか",
		"voice_file": "VOICE_MAIN_223_036_01198",
		"still_path_hash": "1488533364831425921",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 34,
		"localized_name": "レスナ",
		"romanized_name": "Resna",
		"model_path_hash": "6823802507187778884",
		"text": "あ、あの、ジョゼさん。\nさっき、あの人、ジョゼさんのことギヨームって……",
		"voice_file": "VOICE_MAIN_001_036_01199",
		"still_path_hash": "2457375212832216718",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 35,
		"localized_name": "レスナ",
		"romanized_name": "Resna",
		"model_path_hash": "6823802507187778884",
		"text": "その名前って、あの、タイニーさんが探している人の\n名前と一緒で",
		"voice_file": "VOICE_MAIN_001_036_01200",
		"still_path_hash": "2457375212832216718",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 36,
		"localized_name": "ジョゼ",
		"romanized_name": "José",
		"model_path_hash": "0",
		"text": "……あちゃあ、聞こえちゃったのか",
		"voice_file": "VOICE_MAIN_223_036_01201",
		"still_path_hash": "1488533364831425921",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 37,
		"localized_name": "レスナ",
		"romanized_name": "Resna",
		"model_path_hash": "6823802507187778884",
		"text": "っ！",
		"voice_file": "VOICE_MAIN_001_036_01202",
		"still_path_hash": "2457375212832216718",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 38,
		"localized_name": "ジョゼ",
		"romanized_name": "José",
		"model_path_hash": "0",
		"text": "嬢ちゃん、その名前は他言無用だ。\n特に監察官の前ではね。もししゃべったりしたら……",
		"voice_file": "VOICE_MAIN_223_036_01203",
		"still_path_hash": "1488533364831425921",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 39,
		"localized_name": "ジョゼ",
		"romanized_name": "José",
		"model_path_hash": "0",
		"text": "永遠に、そのおしゃべりな口は動かせなくなる。\n俺と嬢ちゃんだけの秘密だ……いいね？",
		"voice_file": "VOICE_MAIN_223_036_01204",
		"still_path_hash": "1488533364831425921",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 40,
		"localized_name": "レスナ",
		"romanized_name": "Resna",
		"model_path_hash": "6823802507187778884",
		"text": "は……はい……",
		"voice_file": "VOICE_MAIN_001_036_01205",
		"still_path_hash": "2457375212832216718",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	}
]